snippet.title: Hyrule Warriors: Age of Calamity - The Game Awards 2020 Spot
snippet.description:
Join the battle to defend Hyrule, 100 years before the events of The Legend of Zelda: Breath of the Wild. Hyrule Warriors: Age of Calamity is available now! If you've already joined the fight, who's your favorite character to battle as?

#HyruleWarriors #Zelda #NintendoSwitch
